# ==============================================================================
# Siterank服务专用 .gcloudignore - 最小化上传文件
# ==============================================================================

# 只上传必需的目录,其他全部排除
*
!services/siterank/**
!pkg/**
!go.work
!go.work.sum

# 排除siterank服务内的非必需文件
services/siterank/scripts/**
!services/siterank/scripts/*.sh
services/siterank/**/*.md
services/siterank/**/*.json
!services/siterank/go.mod
!services/siterank/go.sum

# 排除测试文件
**/*_test.go
**/test*.go

# 排除临时文件
**/*.tmp
**/*.log
**/.DS_Store

# 排除构建产物
**/dist/
**/build/
**/.next/
